
Muchidzidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]], [[gonyaina tsazamativi]] (Rhombus) chiumbwa chine mativi mana ose akaenzana. Gonya dzemukati dzakatarisana dzinenge dzakaenzana zvakare. Chiumbwa ichi chine madanhamakonya maviri anochekana negonya re 90<sup>o</sup>. Tsazano iri pamupanda wegonyaina tsazamativi.


==Zvifaniro zveGonyaina tsazamativi==

Gonyaina tsazamativi rega-rega rine ma[[danhamakonya]] maviri anobatanidza [[hawa]] ''(vertices)'' mbiri dzakatarisana, uye mativi maviri akati [[sambamba]]. Kuchishandiswa [[gonyanhatu]] dzine [[chidzudzani]] pane umbowo hwokuti [[gonyaina tsazamativi]] rine [[kupimirana]] kunotevedza madanhamakonya maviri ari mariri. Chiumbwa ichi chine faniro ''(properties)'' dzinotevera:

* Gonya mbiri dzakatarisana dzakaenzana
* Madanhamakonya maviri anochekana negonya re 90<sup>o</sup>; akaita mutwi.
* Madanhamakonya maviri anochekana kuita zvikamu zviviri zvakaenzana.

Faniro yekutanga inotiudza kuti gonyaina tsazamativi riri pamupanda we[[gonyaina sambamba]] 

==Ruvanze rweGonyaina tsazamativi==

Ruvanze rwechiumbwa ichi runowanikwa netsazaniso inoti:

'''Ruvanze, A  =  1/2.b.h'''

Apa ''b'' anomirira nhambwe yehwaro; ''h'' achimirira nhambwe yehudzamu. Tinotora hwaro sedivi ripi zvaro; hudzamu hunozotorwa senhambwe ye[[mutwi]] unobatanidza mativi maviri asina kutevedzana.

Imwe nzira inokwaniswa kushanda ndeyekuti tinopangidzwa [[hawa]] dzegonyaina iri nemavara ABCD; ruvanze tinenge torwuwana netsazaniso inoti:

'''Ruvanze, A  = (AC.BD)/2'''

Apa ''AC'' na''BD'' dzinenge dziri nhambwe dzemadanhamakonya maviri.
